main event: An unidentified object was reported flying over a house in Oak Park at 11-minute intervals, flashing bluish-white.
interesting points: The object was observed flying north-northwest,It appeared every 11 minutes,Flashing lights were seen during its passage over the house,The object was described as high in the sky,The observer had previously reported incidents to Air Force officials.
witness description: A civilian observer who reported the sighting.
